1.1 Introduction
CampusEye AI is an AI-powered campus problem reporting and triage system designed to help students report real-life campus issues and ensure those issues are handled efficiently.
In many campuses, problems such as water shortages, Wi-Fi failures, sanitation issues, broken equipment, and safety risks are reported informally through chats, friends, or Telegram groups. These reports are often lost, duplicated, or ignored.
Our system transforms these scattered complaints into structured, prioritized, and actionable tasks using Artificial Intelligence.

